%N A015539 Inverse of 1530th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015539 Periodic with period length 1530. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015539 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015539/b015539.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015539 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1530.
%H A015539 <a href="/index/Rec#order_384">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 384.
%H A015539 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015539 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
